prompts.prompt: Create a well styled and beautiful component that lists the comments on a given jira issue. Add a fetch button that fetches the comments for the issue. Use any relevant api or package to connect with jira. Also add a plus button that allows adding a new comment. Add proper error and null handling. Use the jira package https://www.npmjs.com/package/jira-client jira-client package version 8.2.2
